title: President Donald J. Trump Announces Presidential Delegation to Attend the Presidential Inauguration of His Excellency Nayib Bukele of El Salvador â€“ The White House
content:
Statements & Releases			

		Foreign Policy	

Issued on:
May 23, 2019
Today, President Donald J. Trump announced the designation of a Presidential Delegation to San Salvador, El Salvador, to attend the Inauguration of His Excellency Nayib Bukele on June 1, 2019.The Honorable Wilbur Ross, Secretary of Commerce, will lead the delegation.Members of the Presidential Delegation:The Honorable Jean Elizabeth Manes, United States Ambassador to the Republic of El SalvadorMr. David Bohigian, Acting President and Chief Executive Officer, Overseas Private Investment CorporationThe Honorable Kimberly Breier, Assistant Secretary of State for Western Hemisphere Affairs, Department of State
